                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280410-70-off393 t18280410-70-cd394"></join>, 18 ozs. of indigo, value 5s.
            </rs>, the goods of the 
               <persName id="t18280410-70-victim538" type="victimName">
                     <rs id="t18280410-70-viclabel395" type="occupation">United Company of Merchants trading to the East Indies</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280410-70-victim538 t18280410-70-viclabel395"></join>
