                     <interp inst="t18280410-70-person541" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an assistant elder to the Company; this is the same sort of indigo as was in the warehouse.</p>
               <p>The prisoner put in a written defence, stating that the property must have been put into his hat by some of the workmen.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 42.</p>
